END
MACRO 18 "冲动还击" Spell_Shadow_RitualOfSacrifice
/startattack
/cast 还击
/cast [combo:<5,nomybuff:冲动,mypower:<81]突袭
/cast [combo:<5,mybuff:冲动,mypower:<61]突袭
/cast [mybuff:切割<1]切割
/cast [combo:>4,mybuff:血腥气息<2]割裂
/cast [combo:>4,nodebuff:破甲]破甲
/cast [combo:>4,mybuff:血腥气息>8,mybuff:切割>3]剔骨
/cast 邪恶攻击
/cast [mypower:<20,mybuff:剑刃乱舞]冲动
/use [mypower:<15,mybuff:剑刃乱舞,nomybuff:冲动]菊花茶
/cast [targeting:player,type:首领]闪避
/use [myhp:<=45]特效治疗石
/use [myhp:<=40]特效治疗药水
/use [myhp:<=35]诺达纳尔草药茶
END
